    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe the condition of this beauty\u2014it\u2019s practically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one. It's super clean inside and out, and I'm sure you'll fall in love the moment you see it. Come take a look!",
