    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure precise valve timing across the entire power band. Mated to a crisp Getrag six-speed manual, the drivetrain delivers linear power to a variable M differential lock. The chassis has received comprehensive subframe reinforcement to mitigate common fatigue points, maintaining factory-spec torsional rigidity. Riding on fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, the suspension geometry provides an unfiltered connection to the tarmac. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key performance icon.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
