    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless example that truly embodies the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating that makes the deep metallic finish glow. Step inside to find an interior that still retains its original factory scent; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by custom-fit liners from the moment of purchase. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing every preventative maintenance task performed ahead of schedule. Every switch, dial, and feature operates with the crisp precision of a brand-new car. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
