    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2011 BMW M3 Coupe (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen is in concours-level condition, retaining its factory-original paint with zero imperfections. Mechanically, the high-revving powerplant delivers a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral dynamics. This vehicle has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and unmodified suspension geometry. The cabin is pristine, showing no bolster wear or UV degradation. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking a mechanically flawless, analog driving experience.",
